  <h2>Inbound Endpoints</h2>
  <p>
    Receive webhooks from external services like Stripe, GitHub, or Shopify. Runlater stores every event, forwards it to your app with retries, and lets you replay failures from the dashboard.
    No webhook handler code needed &mdash; just point the service at your Runlater inbound URL.
  </p>

