  <h2>Named Queues</h2>
  <p>
    Use the <code class="bg-slate-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">queue</code>
    parameter to serialize execution.
    Tasks in the same named queue run one at a time within your organization — each task waits for the previous one to finish before starting.
    Tasks without a queue (or in different queues) run in parallel as normal.
  </p>

